00:02:24,57 --> 00:02:27,08
after the senseless killing of George Floyd.
这是因 George Floyd 被毫无理由地杀害导致的

29
00:02:27,94 --> 00:02:31,21
And while the events of this past month are sadly not new,
令人难过的是 过去这个月发生的种种事件并非首次

