Of course, over the years, we've kept the fundamentals largely the same
当然 这么多年来 我们没有改变基本要素

120
00:06:13,27 --> 00:06:17,61
but carefully added features like folders for organizing your apps,
但是精心添加了一些十分有用的新功能 例如可以整理 app 的文件夹

121
00:06:17,67 --> 00:06:19,61
widgets for quick information
可以快速查询信息的小组件

123
00:06:19,68 --> 00:06:23,41
and personalized experiences powered by on-device intelligence
由设备端智能技术支持的个性化体验

124
00:06:23,48 --> 00:06:27,08
that serve up just the right thing at just the right moment.
这些功能都在正确的时间 起到了恰到好处的作用

126
00:06:27,15 --> 00:06:30,35
It's hard to imagine iPhone without these features now.
很难想象 如果 iPhone 没有这些功能 情况会如何

128
00:06:30,42 --> 00:06:32,52
Well, that brings us to this year.
让我们聚焦今年推出的新功能吧

129
00:06:32,59 --> 00:06:35,39
We're doing more on our iPhones today than ever before,
我们从未像如今这样 更加依赖于 iPhone 的使用

130
00:06:35,46 --> 00:06:39,46
so we've rethought some of the core elements of iOS to reflect this.
因此 我们重新设计了 iOS 的某些核心元素 让使用更为便捷

132
00:06:39,53 --> 00:06:41,33
Let me give you a quick peek.
我们来一睹其风采吧

133
00:06:42,20 --> 00:06:44,87
["Like This Like That" by BEGINNERS &amp; Night Panda playing]

134
00:07:19,87 --> 00:07:21,54
This is gonna be amazing.
这将是非常棒的体验

